/d/Earthsea/gont/gont_city/rooms/
   equip_shop.c   Sells (only) backpacks, sacks, torches, lamps, purses
   general_shop.c Buys and sells 'used' armour, weapons, equipment
   tavern.c       Sells food and drink, and full bottles of liquor 
                       and grog. Also keys to the back room.
   bank.c         depository, change money
/d/Earthsea/gont/gont_city/rooms/harrekki_room.c
  You can purchase harrekkis here (messengers)

/d/Earthsea/gont/tenalders/village/

  witch_herb_store.c  buys and sells herbs, herb jars, pouches,
                      and lip pomade
  eq_shop.c           sells backpacks, sacks, lamps, torches, purses
  peddler.c           general shop, buys and sells 'used' armour,
                         weapons, and equipment
  pub_room.c          pub sells food and drink

/d/Earthsea/gont/beach/ 
  cliff_rooms/cliff02.c  general shop, buys and sells 'used' armour,
                           weapons, equipment

/d/Earthsea/roke/thwil/
  herb.c              buys and sells herbs, herb jars, pouches
  shop.c              buys and sells 'used' armour, weapons, equipment
  bank.c              depository, change money